title: El Maple
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, International, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Ecuadorian
description: In the Mariscal suburb. Serves a wide range of foods from Ecuadorian in addition to Chinese, Mexican, Italian, and American. Has veggie burgers, fruit smoothies, vegetarian version of Ecuador's national dish, soy steak, white corn, potato cakes, beet root, veggie chorizo sausage. Free wireless internet.
streetAddress: Joaquin Pinto E7-68 y Diego de Almagro, Mariscal
